dy:'<p></p><p><br/><strong>Coupon details</strong><br/><span style="color:#666666">50% off</span><br/><span style="color:#666666">Nomin.spend,max$10off</span><br/><span style="color:#666666">From TikTok Shop</span></p><p><br/><strong>Valid through</strong><br/><span style="color:#666666">Valid for 1 day after claiming</span></p><p><br/><strong>Limitations</strong><br/><span style="color:#666666">For specific seller(s). </span></p><p><br/><strong>Terms and conditions</strong></p><p><span style="color:#666666">New users may be eligible to receive a discont coupon. To claim the coupon, users must complete the in-app verification process first. Eligibility for this promotion is subject to change based on our internal testing protocols or risk control measures. For the most up-to-date information, refer to the in-app TikTok Shop coupon terms.</span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">These coupon terms (the &quot;Coupon Terms&quot;) set out the terms and conditions that apply to any limited time coupon promotions offered by TikTok for eligible user purchases on TikTok Shop on the TikTok platform and any coupons related to returns and/or shipping (collectively, the &quot;TikTok Shop Coupon&quot;). The TikTok entity offering the TikTok Shop Coupons to you is the TikTok entity that provides you with the platform as set out in the TikTok Terms of Service (&quot;we&quot; / &quot;TikTok&quot;). We may may make changes to these Coupon Terms. The &quot;Last Updated&quot; date above indicates when these Coupon Terms were last changed. If we make future changes, we may provide you with notice of such changes, such as by sending an email, providing a notice through our TikTok Shop (or otherservices), or updating the date at the top of these Coupon Terms. Unless we say otherwise in our notice, the amended Coupon Terms will be effective immediately, and your use of any TikTok Shop Coupons after we provide such notice will confirm your acceptance of the changes. Any such changes will not apply to any dispute between you and TikTok arising prior to the date on which we posted the amended Coupon Terms, or otherwise notified you of such changes.    </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">1. Additional terms and conditions (including but not limited to the TikTok Shop Coupon validity period, value, availability, applicability, and eligibility criteria) will accompany and apply to any TikTok Shop Coupons made available to you (&quot;Additional Terms&quot;). In case of any irreconcilable conflict between the Additional Terms and these Coupon Terms, the Additional Terms will prevail.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">2. TikTok does not guarantee that you will receive any TikTokShop Coupons. You must satisfy the Additional Terms communicated to you in order to receive TikTok Shop Coupons.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">3. TikTokShop Coupons can only be used for purchases of eligible products on TikTok Shop, subject to the availability of stock of such eligible products and the terms and exclusions set forth in these Coupon Terms or the Additional Terms made available to you.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">4. TikTokShop Coupons can only be used on TikTok Shop and may not be used on any third-party websites or apps.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">5. To use any TikTok Shop Coupon, you must have an account on the TikTok platform, be offered the TikTok Shop Coupon by TikTok, and be eligible to make a purchase on TikTok Shop in accordance with TikTok Customer Policy. To the extent not already applied to any eligible product(s) in your cart, you must apply the TikTok Shop Coupon during the applicable promotion period specified in the Additional Terms to the eligible product(s) in the purchase cart and follow any relevant instructions provided to you.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">6. Each TikTok Shop Coupon may only be redeemed once against one order of eligible product(s) on TikTok Shop.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">7. We may limit the total number of TikTok Shop Coupons (including &quot;Shipping Coupons&quot;), Seller Coupons (defined below) and other promotional discounts that may be applied to a single product.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">8. If you placed an order from TikTok Shop using a &quot;Shipping Coupon&quot; and applied for a refund after the order was shipped, then you will not be able to use that &quot;Shipping Coupon&quot; again or redeem it for cash, credit or any other form of compensation. Otherwise, if you request a refund for an order from TikTok Shop to which you applied a TikTok Shop Coupon, then (i) the TikTok Shop Coupon discount will be subtracted from the refund you receive, and (ii) you may re-use that TikTok Shop Coupon, subject to these Coupon Terms and any Additional Terms.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">9. If a TikTok Shop Coupon is granted to you (or you are entitled to a TikTok Shop Coupon) as a result of a previous order you have placed, and this previous order is refunded or otherwise canceled for any reason, then the TikTok Shop Coupon granted to you will become void and invalid (and you will no longer be entitled to use such TikTok Shop Coupon).   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">10. TikTokShop Coupons are non-transferable and non-exchangeable and may not be redeemed for cash, credit or any other form of compensation.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">11. If any TikTok Shop Coupons, or the grant of any TikTok Shop Coupons, are prohibited in the jurisdiction in which you are based, such TikTok Shop Coupons will be void.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">12. You will be responsible for the payment of any applicable taxes related to your receipt or use of any TikTok Shop Coupons. TikTok will have no liability to you for any such taxes.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">13. Sellers on TikTok Shop may offer their own Coupons to you, as notified and indicated on the coupons to you by the relevant seller (&quot;Seller Coupons&quot;). Your use of a Seller Coupon is between you and the relevant seller and that seller will be solely responsible for that Seller Coupon. To the extent permitted under applicable law in your jurisdiction, a seller may withdraw or cancel Seller Coupons and, in such circumstances, that seller will be solely responsible and liable for any such withdrawal or cancellation. You and the seller are responsible for resolving any dispute in relation to your use of Seller Coupons between you and sellers. TikTok may facilitate communications between you and sellers, but TikTok is not a party to any such dispute and has no obligation to participate in the discussions or resolution for such dispute.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">14. TikTokShop Coupons may be used in conjunction with Seller Coupons, subject to Section 7 of these Coupon Terms and any applicable Additional Terms. If you are entitled to use a Seller Coupon and TikTok Shop coupon for the same product, then you will only be entitled to use the TikTok Shop Coupon after you have already applied and benefited from any price reduction offered by the Seller Coupon on that product.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">15. If an order from TikTok Shop that you applied a Seller Coupon to is refunded then (i) the Seller Coupon discount will be subtracted from the refund you receive, and (ii)you may be able to re-use that Seller Coupon, subject to rules for the Seller Coupon as set up by the sellers.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">16. TikTok may withdraw or cancel any TikTok Shop Coupon granted to you, or withhold any TikTok Shop Coupon you may otherwise be entitled to receive, in its reasonable discretion, including if TikTok detects any activities conducted by you in material violation of TikTok&#x27;s applicable terms and policies (for example, fraud or illegal activity).   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">17. These Coupon Terms are governed in accordance with, and all disputes arising out of or in connection with these Coupon Terms will be subject to the applicable &quot;Governing Law and Jurisdiction&quot; provisions of the TikTok Terms of Service.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">18. You can contact TikTok by emailing e-commerce@tiktok.com or reaching out to our customer service if you have any questions connected to these Coupon Terms or a TikTok Shop Coupon. Please contact the relevant seller regarding any questions connected to Seller Coupons.</span></span></p>',remBody:'<p></p><p><br/><strong>Coupon details</strong><br/><span style="color:#666666">50% off</span><br/><span style="color:#666666">Nomin.spend,max$10off</span><br/><span style="color:#666666">From TikTok Shop</span></p><p><br/><strong>Valid through</strong><br/><span style="color:#666666">Valid for 1 day after claiming</span></p><p><br/><strong>Limitations</strong><br/><span style="color:#666666">For specific seller(s). </span></p><p><br/><strong>Terms and conditions</strong></p><p><span style="color:#666666">New users may be eligible to receive a discont coupon. To claim the coupon, users must complete the in-app verification process first. Eligibility for this promotion is subject to change based on our internal testing protocols or risk control measures. For the most up-to-date information, refer to the in-app TikTok Shop coupon terms.</span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">These coupon terms (the &quot;Coupon Terms&quot;) set out the terms and conditions that apply to any limited time coupon promotions offered by TikTok for eligible user purchases on TikTok Shop on the TikTok platform and any coupons related to returns and/or shipping (collectively, the &quot;TikTok Shop Coupon&quot;). The TikTok entity offering the TikTok Shop Coupons to you is the TikTok entity that provides you with the platform as set out in the TikTok Terms of Service (&quot;we&quot; / &quot;TikTok&quot;). We may may make changes to these Coupon Terms. The &quot;Last Updated&quot; date above indicates when these Coupon Terms were last changed. If we make future changes, we may provide you with notice of such changes, such as by sending an email, providing a notice through our TikTok Shop (or otherservices), or updating the date at the top of these Coupon Terms. Unless we say otherwise in our notice, the amended Coupon Terms will be effective immediately, and your use of any TikTok Shop Coupons after we provide such notice will confirm your acceptance of the changes. Any such changes will not apply to any dispute between you and TikTok arising prior to the date on which we posted the amended Coupon Terms, or otherwise notified you of such changes.    </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">1. Additional terms and conditions (including but not limited to the TikTok Shop Coupon validity period, value, availability, applicability, and eligibility criteria) will accompany and apply to any TikTok Shop Coupons made available to you (&quot;Additional Terms&quot;). In case of any irreconcilable conflict between the Additional Terms and these Coupon Terms, the Additional Terms will prevail.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">2. TikTok does not guarantee that you will receive any TikTokShop Coupons. You must satisfy the Additional Terms communicated to you in order to receive TikTok Shop Coupons.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">3. TikTokShop Coupons can only be used for purchases of eligible products on TikTok Shop, subject to the availability of stock of such eligible products and the terms and exclusions set forth in these Coupon Terms or the Additional Terms made available to you.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">4. TikTokShop Coupons can only be used on TikTok Shop and may not be used on any third-party websites or apps.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">5. To use any TikTok Shop Coupon, you must have an account on the TikTok platform, be offered the TikTok Shop Coupon by TikTok, and be eligible to make a purchase on TikTok Shop in accordance with TikTok Customer Policy. To the extent not already applied to any eligible product(s) in your cart, you must apply the TikTok Shop Coupon during the applicable promotion period specified in the Additional Terms to the eligible product(s) in the purchase cart and follow any relevant instructions provided to you.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">6. Each TikTok Shop Coupon may only be redeemed once against one order of eligible product(s) on TikTok Shop.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">7. We may limit the total number of TikTok Shop Coupons (including &quot;Shipping Coupons&quot;), Seller Coupons (defined below) and other promotional discounts that may be applied to a single product.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">8. If you placed an order from TikTok Shop using a &quot;Shipping Coupon&quot; and applied for a refund after the order was shipped, then you will not be able to use that &quot;Shipping Coupon&quot; again or redeem it for cash, credit or any other form of compensation. Otherwise, if you request a refund for an order from TikTok Shop to which you applied a TikTok Shop Coupon, then (i) the TikTok Shop Coupon discount will be subtracted from the refund you receive, and (ii) you may re-use that TikTok Shop Coupon, subject to these Coupon Terms and any Additional Terms.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">9. If a TikTok Shop Coupon is granted to you (or you are entitled to a TikTok Shop Coupon) as a result of a previous order you have placed, and this previous order is refunded or otherwise canceled for any reason, then the TikTok Shop Coupon granted to you will become void and invalid (and you will no longer be entitled to use such TikTok Shop Coupon).   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">10. TikTokShop Coupons are non-transferable and non-exchangeable and may not be redeemed for cash, credit or any other form of compensation.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">11. If any TikTok Shop Coupons, or the grant of any TikTok Shop Coupons, are prohibited in the jurisdiction in which you are based, such TikTok Shop Coupons will be void.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">12. You will be responsible for the payment of any applicable taxes related to your receipt or use of any TikTok Shop Coupons. TikTok will have no liability to you for any such taxes.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">13. Sellers on TikTok Shop may offer their own Coupons to you, as notified and indicated on the coupons to you by the relevant seller (&quot;Seller Coupons&quot;). Your use of a Seller Coupon is between you and the relevant seller and that seller will be solely responsible for that Seller Coupon. To the extent permitted under applicable law in your jurisdiction, a seller may withdraw or cancel Seller Coupons and, in such circumstances, that seller will be solely responsible and liable for any such withdrawal or cancellation. You and the seller are responsible for resolving any dispute in relation to your use of Seller Coupons between you and sellers. TikTok may facilitate communications between you and sellers, but TikTok is not a party to any such dispute and has no obligation to participate in the discussions or resolution for such dispute.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">14. TikTokShop Coupons may be used in conjunction with Seller Coupons, subject to Section 7 of these Coupon Terms and any applicable Additional Terms. If you are entitled to use a Seller Coupon and TikTok Shop coupon for the same product, then you will only be entitled to use the TikTok Shop Coupon after you have already applied and benefited from any price reduction offered by the Seller Coupon on that product.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">15. If an order from TikTok Shop that you applied a Seller Coupon to is refunded then (i) the Seller Coupon discount will be subtracted from the refund you receive, and (ii)you may be able to re-use that Seller Coupon, subject to rules for the Seller Coupon as set up by the sellers.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">16. TikTok may withdraw or cancel any TikTok Shop Coupon granted to you, or withhold any TikTok Shop Coupon you may otherwise be entitled to receive, in its reasonable discretion, including if TikTok detects any activities conducted by you in material violation of TikTok&#x27;s applicable terms and policies (for example, fraud or illegal activity).   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">17. These Coupon Terms are governed in accordance with, and all disputes arising out of or in connection with these Coupon Terms will be subject to the applicable &quot;Governing Law and Jurisdiction&quot; provisions of the TikTok Terms of Service.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">18. You can contact TikTok by emailing e-commerce@tiktok.com or reaching out to our customer service if you have any questions connected to these Coupon Terms or a TikTok Shop Coupon. Please contact the relevant seller regarding any questions connected to Seller Coupons.</span></span></p>',raw:'\n    <!Doctype html>\n    <html>\n      \n    <head>\n      <meta charset="UTF-8">\n      <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, minimum-scale=1, user-scalable=no">\n      <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">\n      <meta name="description" content="">\n      <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">\n      <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="default">\n      <meta name="screen-orientation" content="portrait">\n      <meta name="x5-orientation" content="portrait">\n      <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=Edge;chrome=1">\n      <link href="https://sf-mis.ttwstatic.com/obj/mis-draft-sg/draft-theme/draft.css?d=1749712139143" rel="stylesheet">\n      <link rel="shortcut icon" href="../favicon.ico">\n      <title>coupon iterms</title>\n      <script>\n      !function(e){function t(){var t=l.getBoundingClientRect().width;375<t/n&&(t=375*n),t/=16,l.style.fontSize=t+"px",e.rem=t}function i(e,t,i,n){var a;return function(){var r=n||this,o=arguments,d=i&&!