-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">2. TikTok does not guarantee that you will receive any TikTokShop Coupons. You must satisfy the Additional Terms communicated to you in order to receive TikTok Shop Coupons.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">3. TikTokShop Coupons can only be used for purchases of eligible products on TikTok Shop, subject to the availability of stock of such eligible products and the terms and exclusions set forth in these Coupon Terms or the Additional Terms made available to you.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">4. TikTokShop Coupons can only be used on TikTok Shop and may not be used on any third-party websites or apps.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">5. To use any TikTok Shop Coupon, you must have an account on the TikTok platform, be offered the TikTok Shop Coupon by TikTok, and be eligible to make a purchase on TikTok Shop in accordance with TikTok Customer Policy. To the extent not already applied to any eligible product(s) in your cart, you must apply the TikTok Shop Coupon during the applicable promotion period specified in the Additional Terms to the eligible product(s) in the purchase cart and follow any relevant instructions provided to you.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">6. Each TikTok Shop Coupon may only be redeemed once against one order of eligible product(s) on TikTok Shop.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">7. We may limit the total number of TikTok Shop Coupons (including &quot;Shipping Coupons&quot;), Seller Coupons (defined below) and other promotional discounts that may be applied to a single product.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">8. If you placed an order from TikTok Shop using a &quot;Shipping Coupon&quot; and applied for a refund after the order was shipped, then you will not be able to use that &quot;Shipping Coupon&quot; again or redeem it for cash, credit or any other form of compensation. Otherwise, if you request a refund for an order from TikTok Shop to which you applied a TikTok Shop Coupon, then (i) the TikTok Shop Coupon discount will be subtracted from the refund you receive, and (ii) you may re-use that TikTok Shop Coupon, subject to these Coupon Terms and any Additional Terms.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">9. If a TikTok Shop Coupon is granted to you (or you are entitled to a TikTok Shop Coupon) as a result of a previous order you have placed, and this previous order is refunded or otherwise canceled for any reason, then the TikTok Shop Coupon granted to you will become void and invalid (and you will no longer be entitled to use such TikTok Shop Coupon).   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">10. TikTokShop Coupons are non-transferable and non-exchangeable and may not be redeemed for cash, credit or any other form of compensation.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">11. If any TikTok Shop Coupons, or the grant of any TikTok Shop Coupons, are prohibited in the jurisdiction in which you are based, such TikTok Shop Coupons will be void.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">12. You will be responsible for the payment of any applicable taxes related to your receipt or use of any TikTok Shop Coupons. TikTok will have no liability to you for any such taxes.   </span></span></p><p><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><span style="color:#666666">13. Sellers on TikTok Shop may offer their own Coupons to you, as notified and indicated on the coupons to you by the relevant seller (&quot;Seller Coupons&quot;). Your use of 