okShop Coupons can only be used for purchases of eligible products on TikTok Shop, subject to the availability of stock of such eligible products and the terms and exclusions set forth in these Coupon Terms or the Additional Terms made available to you. 4. TikTokShop Coupons can only be used on TikTok Shop and may not be used on any third-party websites or apps. 5. To use any TikTok Shop Coupon, you must have an account on the TikTok platform, be offered the TikTok Shop Coupon by TikTok, and be eligible to make a purchase on TikTok Shop in accordance with TikTok Customer Policy. To the extent not already applied to any eligible product(s) in your cart, you must apply the TikTok Shop Coupon during the applicable promotion period specified in the Additional Terms to the eligible product(s) in the purchase cart and follow any relevant instructions provided to you. 6. Each TikTok Shop Coupon may only be redeemed once against one order of eligible product(s) on TikTok Shop. 7. We may limit the total number of TikTok Shop Coupons (including "Shipping Coupons"), Seller Coupons (defined below) and other promotional discounts that may be applied to a single product. 8. If you placed an order from TikTok Shop using a "Shipping Coupon" and applied for a refund after the order was shipped, then you will not be able to use that "Shipping Coupon" again or redeem it for cash, credit or any other form of compensation. Otherwise, if you request a refund for an order from TikTok Shop to which you applied a TikTok Shop Coupon, then (i) the TikTok Shop Coupon discount will be subtracted from the refund you receive, and (ii) you may re-use that TikTok Shop Coupon, subject to these Coupon Terms and any Additional Terms. 9. If a TikTok Shop Coupon is granted to you (or you are entitled to a TikTok Shop Coupon) as a result of a previous order you have placed, and this previous order is refunded or otherwise canceled for any reason, then the TikTok Shop Coupon granted to you will become void and invalid (and you will no longer be entitled to use such TikTok Shop Coupon). 10. TikTokShop Coupons are non-transferable and  non-exchangeable and may not be redeemed for cash, credit or any other form of compensation. 11. If any TikTok Shop Coupons, or the grant of any TikTok Shop Coupons, are prohibited in the jurisdiction in which you are based, such TikTok Shop Coupons will be void. 12. You will be responsible for the payment of any applicable taxes related to your receipt or use of any TikTok Shop Coupons. TikTok will have no liability to you for any such taxes. 13. Sellers on TikTok Shop may offer their own Coupons to you, as notified and indicated on the coupons to you by the relevant seller ("Seller Coupons"). Your use of a Seller Coupon is between you and the relevant seller and that seller will be solely responsible for that Seller Coupon. To the extent permitted under applicable law in your jurisdiction, a seller may withdraw or cancel Seller Coupons and, in such circumstances, that seller will be solely responsible and liable for any such withdrawal or cancellation. You and the seller are responsible for resolving any dispute in relation to your use of Seller Coupons between you and sellers. TikTok may facilitate communications between you and sellers, but TikTok is not a party to any such dispute and has no obligation to participate in the discussions or resolution for such dispute. 14. TikTokShop Coupons may be used in conjunction with Seller Coupons, subject to Section 7 of these Coupon Terms and any applicable Additional Terms. If you are entitled to use a Seller Coupon and TikTok Shop coupon for the same product, then you will only be entitled to use the TikTok Shop Coupon after you have already applied and benefited from any price reduction offered by the Seller Coupon on that product. 15. If an order from TikTok Shop that you applied a Seller Coupon to is refunded then (i) the Seller Coupon discount will be subtracted from the refund you rec